4. TRADE SECRETS

The Software contains trade secrets and confidential proprietary information
belonging to the Owners. The Software's source code, algorithms, data models,
AI prompts, system architecture, and business logic constitute trade secrets
under the Louisiana Uniform Trade Secrets Act, La. R.S. 51:1431(4), and the
Defend Trade Secrets Act, 18 U.S.C. § 1839(3). Unauthorized disclosure,
misappropriation, or use of these trade secrets is strictly prohibited and
subject to civil and criminal liability.

5. AI-GENERATED CONTENT AND DATA

All AI-generated outputs, including but not limited to property listings,
